-- Slovenian Agencies Seek Buyer for Splosna Plovba Shipping Stake
-- B y   B o r i s   C e r n i
-- 2012-01-06T12:21:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-06/slovenian-agencies-seek-buyer-for-splosna-plovba-shipping-stake.html
Slovenia’s Kapitalska druzba d.d. and
Slovenska odskodninska druzba d.d. are seeking a buyer for a 25
percent holding in Splosna Plovba d.o.o., the country’s shipping
company that is majority owned by  Germany ’s Peter Doehle
Schiffarts KG.  The two state-owned companies said today in an e-mailed
statement from Ljubljana said they are seeking bids of more than
60 million euros ($77 million).  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Cerni in Ljubljana at 
 bcerni@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
